---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---
<Layout title="Learn More">
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Learn more about your chatbot</title>
  <style>
    #learn-more {
      background-color: #f0f4ee; 
      color: #3c3f36; 
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h1 {
      color: #4b6f4e; 
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #4b6f4e; 
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    ul {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    li {
      background: #d0e6d4; 
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding: 10px;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    li:hover {
      background: #c2e2c2; 
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="w-full max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-20 mt-36" id="learn-more">
    <h1 class="text-3xl text-pretty">Meet Roy, our interactive chatbot</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg">
      Let yourself be helped to have a healthier life, thanks to this interactive chatbot that takes into account your mood.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Key features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <h2>Intelligent conversations</h2>
          <p>Engage in natural conversations with the bot using either voice or text chat. Our advanced AI understands your input and responds accordingly.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h2>Emotion recognition</h2>
          <p>The bot has the capability to recognize your emotions. Based on your feelings, it can recommend personalized music, recipes, and artistic content that resonate with your current mood.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h2>Personalized profile</h2>
          <p>Create your own profile where you can save your favorite content, including music playlists, recipes you love, and artworks that inspire you.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h2>Customizable experience</h2>
          <p>Tailor the appearance of your profile and the application to suit your preferences. Adjust colors and layouts to create a user experience that feels uniquely yours.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h2>Blog and social interaction</h2>
          <p>Stay connected with the community! Follow other users, view their shared content in the blog section, and interact with them to exchange ideas and recommendations.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h2>Bot Features overview</h2>
          <p>Get to know the capabilities of your AI assistant. Explore how it can enhance your daily life by providing suggestions that fit your unique lifestyle.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>

      Join us in this innovative journey and let Roy enrich your everyday experiences with meaningful interactions and personalized recommendations!
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">How It Works</h2>
      <p>
        Interact with your bot anytime you need assistance. Whether you're looking for a new recipe, a song to match your mood, or inspiration from the art world, your bot is here to help.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>

</Layout>